    <item>
      <title>消费者物价指数 (CPI)、零售销售报告推动美联储降息，国债飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/treasuries-soar-as-traders-see-easing-inflation-aiding-fed-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[良好的通胀数据和弱于预期的零售销售数据促使交易员提高了对美联储今年降息的预期，美国国债上涨，导致10年期国债收益率跌至一个多月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/treasuries-soar-as-traders-see-easing-inflation-aiding-fed-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 12:42:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国核心消费者物价指数六个月来首次降温，为美联储带来缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/us-core-cpi-decelerated-in-april-for-first-time-in-six-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[衡量美国潜在通胀的一项指标在 4 月份出现了六个月以来的首次降温，对于希望今年开始降息的美联储官员来说，这是朝着正确方向迈出的一小步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/us-core-cpi-decelerated-in-april-for-first-time-in-six-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 12:33:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
